#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.22:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga"
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 22. Ciraṭṭhitisutta → ṭhitisuttaṃ (bj) | ṭhiti (pts1)
msgctxt "sn47.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Ciraṭṭhitisutta"
msgstr "22. Long Lasting"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.22:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ."
msgstr "The same setting."

msgctxt "sn47.22:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā bhaddo āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn47.22:1.3"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho, āvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena tathāgate parinibbute "
"saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti?"
msgstr ""
"“What is the cause, Reverend Ānanda, what is the reason why the true "
"teaching does not last long after the final extinguishment of the Realized "
"One?"

msgctxt "sn47.22:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ko panāvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo "
"ciraṭṭhitiko hotī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What is the cause, what is the reason why the true teaching does last long "
"after the final extinguishment of the Realized One?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.22:2.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, āvuso bhadda."
msgstr "“Good, good, Reverend Bhadda!"

msgctxt "sn47.22:2.2"
msgid ""
"Bhaddako kho te, āvuso bhadda, ummaṅgo, bhaddakaṃ paṭibhānaṃ, kalyāṇī "
"paripucchā."
msgstr "Your approach and articulation are excellent, and it’s a good question."

msgctxt "sn47.22:2.3"
msgid "Evañhi tvaṃ, āvuso bhadda, pucchasi:"
msgstr "For you asked:"

msgctxt "sn47.22:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘ko nu kho, āvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena tathāgate parinibbute "
"saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti?"
msgstr ""
"‘What is the cause, Reverend Ānanda, what is the reason why the true "
"teaching does not last long after the final extinguishment of the Realized "
"One?"

msgctxt "sn47.22:2.5"
msgid ""
"Ko panāvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo "
"ciraṭṭhitiko hotī’”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What is the cause, what is the reason why the true teaching does last long "
"after the final extinguishment of the Realized One?’”"

msgctxt "sn47.22:2.6"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, reverend.”"

msgctxt "sn47.22:2.7"
msgid ""
"“Catunnaṃ kho, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā tathāgate "
"parinibbute saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"“It’s because of not developing and cultivating the four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation that the true teaching doesn’t last long after the "
"final extinguishment of the Realized One."

msgctxt "sn47.22:2.8"
msgid ""
"Catunnañca kho, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā tathāgate "
"parinibbute saddhammo ciraṭṭhitiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of developing and cultivating the four kinds of mindfulness "
"meditation that the true teaching does last long after the final "
"extinguishment of the Realized One."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.22:3.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.22:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idhāvuso, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya "
"loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.22:3.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.22:3.4"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.22:3.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.22:3.6"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā "
"tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of not developing and cultivating these four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation that the true teaching doesn’t last long after the "
"final extinguishment of the Realized One."

msgctxt "sn47.22:3.7"
msgid ""
"Imesañca kho, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo ciraṭṭhitiko hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness "
"meditation that the true teaching does last long after the final "
"extinguishment of the Realized One.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.22:3.8"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
